<html
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
  xml:lang="en"
  lang="en"
  metal:use-macro="context/@@main_template/master"
  i18n:domain="launchpad">

<body>

<metal:leftportlets fill-slot="portlets_one">
  <div tal:replace="structure context/@@+portlet-attendees" />
</metal:leftportlets>

<metal:rightportlets fill-slot="portlets_two">
  <div tal:replace="structure context/@@+portlet-details" />
</metal:rightportlets>

<metal:heading fill-slot="pageheading">
  <h3 tal:content="context/title">Sprint Title</h3>
</metal:heading>

<div metal:fill-slot="main">

  <div metal:use-macro="context/@@launchpad_form/form">

    <h1 metal:fill-slot="heading">Register someone else</h1>

    <div metal:fill-slot="extra_info" class="documentDescription">
      Use this form to register someone else to attend the meeting.
      Use the sprint's local time.
    </div>

  </div>

</div>

<div metal:fill-slot="help">
<p>If you know that someone is attending the sprint, but has not yet
registered themselves, you can register them here.</p>

<p>The times should be entered in the local time for the location of
the sprint, which is
<kbd tal:content="context/time_zone">UTC</kbd>.</p>
</div>
    
</body>
</html>

